high_descs: turn to face the bath tub
pick up a pink bar of soap on the right from the tub ledge
turn to walk to face the left sink
wash the soap in the sink, pick up the soap from the sink
walk to face the bath tub
put the soap into the tub basin
anns.task_desc: put a washed bar of soap into a bath tub

high_descs: Walk forward towards the counter, then turn left and go up to the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap that is to the right of the other bar of soap on the tub.
Turn around completely, walk a few steps, then turn left to face the bathroom sink closest to the tub.
Rinse off the bar of soap in the sink before taking it back out.
Turn around completely, then turn right to go back to the tub.
Place the bar of soap down in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a wet bar of soap in the bathtub.

high_descs: Walk up to the sink and turn left to face the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap on the right at the edge of the tub.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Place the bar of soap inside of the sink, rinse off the bar of soap with water, pick up the bar of soap from the sink.
Turn left and walk over to the tub.
Place the bar of soap inside of the tub in front of the drain.
anns.task_desc: To rinse off a bar of soap and place the soap in the tub.
